    "monster6653": "<h1 class=monster>Ancient Tornado Dragon<br><span class=type>Huge elemental magical beast (air, dragon)</span><br><span class=level>Level 23 Elite Lurker<span class=xp> XP 10200</span></span></h1><table class=bodytable><tr><td><b>HP</b> 338; <b>Bloodied</b> 169<td class=rightalign><b>Initiative</b> +24<tr><td><b>AC</b> 36, <b>Fortitude</b> 34, <b>Reflex</b> 35, <b>Will</b> 33<td class=rightalign><b>Perception</b>+17<tr><td><b>Speed</b> 10, fly 10 (hover)<td class=rightalign>Darkvision<tr><td colspan=2><b>Saving Throws</b> +2; <b>Action Points</b> 1</table><h2>Traits</h2><p class='flavor alt'>☼ <b>Whirling Winds</b> ✦ <b>Aura</b> 1</p><p class=flavorIndent>The dragon has partial concealment against any enemy in the aura.</p><h2>Standard Actions</h2><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Bite</b> (cold) ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Attack:</i> Melee 3 (one creature); +28 vs. AC</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Hit:</i> 2d10 + 9 damage plus 2d10 cold damage.</p><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Claw</b> (lightning) ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Attack:</i> Melee 2 (one creature); +28 vs. AC</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Hit:</i> 2d6 + 9 damage, and ongoing 15 lightning damage (save ends).</p><p class='flavor alt'>⚔ <b>Double Attack</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Effect:</i> The dragon uses bite and claw or uses claw twice.</p><p class='flavor alt'>ᗕ <b>Blinding Wind</b> (cold, thunder) ✦ Recharge ⚄ ⚅</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Attack:</i> Close blast 5 (creatures in the blast); +26 vs. Fortitude</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Hit:</i> 3d12 + 7 cold and thunder damage, and the target is blinded until the end of the dragon's next turn.</p><h2>Minor Actions</h2><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Expanding Aura</b> ✦ <b>Recharge</b> when the dragon starts its turn and its whirling winds is smaller than aura 5</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Effect:</i> The whirling winds aura expands by 2 squares.</p><p class='flavor alt'>⚔ <b>Twister Unleashed</b> ✦ <b>Recharge</b> when the dragon starts its turn and its whirling winds is aura 5</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Effect:</i> Any effect on the dragon that includes the immobilized, restrained, or slowed condition ends. The dragon becomes insubstantial and shifts up to its speed, and it can move through enemies' spaces. Each time the dragon enters an enemy's space for the first time during this movement, it can use bite against that enemy. On a hit, the dragon slides the target up to 5 squares, and the target falls prone.</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Effect:</i> The dragon's whirling winds reverts to aura 1.</p><h2>Triggered Actions</h2><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Storm Twist</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Trigger:</i> The dragon takes lightning or thunder damage.</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Effect (Opportunity Action):</i> The dragon becomes insubstantial and can shift up to its speed.</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Str</b> 24 (+18)                <b>Dex</b> 28 (+20)                <b>Wis</b> 23 (+17)<br><b>Con</b> 25 (+18)                <b>Int</b> 20 (+16)                <b>Cha</b> 20 (+16)</p><p class=flavor><b>Alignment</b> Evil       <b> Languages</b> Common, Draconic, Primordial</p><p class=publishedIn>Published in Dragon Magazine 425.</p>",
